      <title>优化</title>
      <link href="/optimize/index.html"/>
      <url>/optimize/index.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>已完成</h1><div class="timeline undefined"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2022</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>08-12</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>pages顶部图片透明  </li><li>整体footer透明</li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>08-13</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>导航页的优化</li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>08-14</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>页脚养鱼    <details class="toggle" ><summary class="toggle-button" style="">具体操作</summary><div class="toggle-content"><p>先引入jquery</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启pjax</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">defer</span> <span class="attr">data-pjax</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xiabo2/CDN@latest/fishes.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>未开启pjax</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>  <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/xiabo2/CDN@latest/fishes.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最终效果在本页面页脚<br>若要更换为彩色鱼则将src改为</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">src=&quot;https://uuuuu.cf/js/fishes.js&quot; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></details> </li><li>配置vscode代码块代码</li><li>标签外挂(Tag plugins)的使用</li><li>修改博客字体   <details class="toggle" ><summary class="toggle-button" style="">效果对比</summary><div class="toggle-content"><p>原字体<br><img src="/img/%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C.png"><br>zhuziAwa1n字体<br><img src="/img/zhuziAwa1n%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C.png"></p></div></details></li></ul></div></div></div><h1>计划</h1><blockquote><p>咕咕咕 </p></blockquote><ul><li>加入文章搜索  </li><li>各部分内容的补充</li></ul>]]></content>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
